ARGUMENT: {'This keeps your full core bundle intact and remains within the 3624 effort LIMIT (total effort 3616).', 'It replaces the two add-ons (A04 + C17) with a single add-on (C54) while still fitting under the limit.', 'If A04 or C17 are must-haves for you, we can instead finalize your add-on version.'}

